LW4/Reader version 0.01
=======================

Read Lightwright 4 files into data structures for manipulation and 
processing by perl. As of this writing, Lightwright is not available
for POSIX compliant operating systems, and so this provides a handy
interface for processing those files on linux.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

